# [SCHC](../wg/schc.html)

## Summary
The SCHC Interim meeting on May 7, 2024, focused on status updates for active working group documents and a detailed presentation on the advancement of the SCHC Architecture. The primary technical discussion centered on refining architectural definitions (Endpoint, Instance, Stratum, Session) and addressing the challenge of routing SCHC datagrams to specific instances when underlying network discriminators are absent.

